of my flesh?"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I wish that my words were written down,"},{"kind":"text","text":" that they were recorded on a scroll"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"or were inscribed in stone forever"},{"kind":"text","text":" by an iron stylus and lead!"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But I know that my Redeemer lives, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or know my living Redeemer"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 16:19","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 23:11","book":"Pro","chapter":23,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 50:34","book":"Jer","chapter":50,"verse":34,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and at the end he will stand on the dust. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 44:6","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 48:12","book":"Isa","chapter":48,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:17–18","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":17,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 16:19","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":19},{"label":"Pr 23:11","book":"Pro","chapter":23,"verse":11},{"label":"Jr 50:34","book":"Jer","chapter":50,"verse":34},{"label":"Is 44:6","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 48:12","book":"Isa","chapter":48,"verse":12},{"label":"Rv 1:17–18","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or know my living Redeemer"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Even after my skin has been destroyed, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit skin which they destroyed, or skin they destroyed in this way"},{"kind":"text","text":" yet I will see God in "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or apart from"},{"kind":"text","text":" my flesh. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 17:15","book":"Psa","chapter":17,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 6:1","book":"Isa","chapter":6,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 13:12","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":12,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 17:15","book":"Psa","chapter":17,"verse":15},{"label":"Is 6:1","book":"Isa","chapter":6,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 13:12","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit skin which they destroyed, or skin they destroyed in this way"},{"marker":1,"text":"Or apart from"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will see him myself;"},{"kind":"text","text":" my eyes will look at him, and not as a stranger. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or not a stranger"},{"kind":"text","text":" My heart longs "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit My kidneys grow faint"},{"kind":"text","text":" within me. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 73:26","book":"Psa","chapter":73,"verse":26,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 84:2","book":"Psa","chapter":84,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 119:81","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":81,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 73:26","book":"Psa","chapter":73,"verse":26},{"label":"Ps 84:2","book":"Psa","chapter":84,"verse":2},{"label":"Ps 119:81","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":81}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or not a stranger"},{"marker":1,"text":"Lit My kidneys grow faint"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If you say, “How will we pursue him,"},{"kind":"text","text":" since the root of the problem lies with him?” "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, LXX, Vg; other Hb mss read me"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss, LXX, Vg; other Hb mss read me"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:19:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"then